overview: On November 12th House of Glory Wrestling presents Born Again live from NYC Arena! The event features the fight between the Amazing Red and Will Ospreay. Also on the card is House of Glory Crown Jewel Champion TJP vs Low Ki vs Charles Mason, Ken Broadway vs Rocky Romero, Ivellise Velez vs Violette, Ace Austin vs Smiley vs Joey Silver vs Nolo Kitano vs Mighty Mante vs Encore and more.
title: HOG: Born Again
